OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 15 JUN
OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1953FLive television pictures are
OL,7,Frelayed from a ship at sea for the
OL,8,Ffirst time during the Coronation Review
OL,9,Fof the Fleet on BBC TV.
OL,10,
OL,11,CG1964FThe final edition of Impromptu
OL,12,Fairs on BBC Two. Unscripted comedy
OL,13,Fshow, devised by David Croft. Hosted by
OL,14,FJeremy Hawk. With Lance Percival,
OL,15,FVictor Spinetti, Peter Reeves, Anne
OL,16,FCunningham, Betty Impey, Joe Melia, and
OL,17,Fwith dance by Una Stubbs.
OL,18,
OL,19,CG1971FMidlands Today is broadcast from
OL,20,Fthe new Pebble Mill studios for the
OL,21,Ffirst time.
OL,22,
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
