OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1983FThe first episode of The Black
OL,7,FAdder airs on BBC One. The initial
OL,8,Fseries of six episodes was written by
OL,9,FRichard Curtis and Rowan Atkinson. The
OL,10,Fidea for the show was conceived while
OL,11,FAtkinson and Curtis were working on Not
OL,12,Fthe Nine o'Clock News. Ben Elton took
OL,13,Fover from Atkinson as co-writer on
OL,14,Fsubsequent series.
