OL,5,
OL,6,CG2020FThe final BBC-sponsored edition
OL,7,Fof Eggheads airs on BBC Two. New
OL,8,Feditions of the programme aired on
OL,9,FChannel 5 from 2021.
OL,10,
OL,11,CG2023FBlackadder: the Lost Pilot airs
OL,12,Fon Gold. Marking the 40th anniversary,
OL,13,FSir Tony Robinson introduces the pilot,
OL,14,Ffilmed in 1982, in which the part of
OL,15,FBaldrick was played by Philip Fox.
